OCCI
----

Resource and Links (base Entity)

Kind (basic) and Mixin (composed) and Action (base Category)

Kind is a type identifier, unique

Mixin are associated to Resource instances _only_

Categorizatiom scheme start with http://schemas.ogf.org/occi/


OCCI Architecture
-----------------

Resource
	summary:
  Compute
	  occi.compute.architecture:
		occi.compute.cores:
		occi.compute.hostname:
		occi.compute.speed:
		occi.compute.memory:
		occi.compute.state:
	Network
	  occi.network.vlan:
	  occi.network.label:
	  occi.network.state:
	Storage
	  occi.storage.size:
	  occi.storage.state:
Link
  StorageLink
	  occi.storagelink.deviceid:
		occi.storagelink.mountpoint:
		occi.storagelink.state:
	NetworkInterface
	  occi.networkinterface.interface:
	  occi.networkinterface.mac:
	  occi.networkinterface.state:
